        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "it's well-known that the Lasombra are hard on their childer - they winnow out the weak with difficult fledgeling periods.  But your sire went above and beyond, and the cruelty, brutality, and harassment didn't stop even after you were initiated and became True Sabbat.  You'd always been a bit of a dreamer - it's hard to see spirits like you do and not get that way.  Your sire thought you were soft, though. Your sire was mistaken.  But the bonds of the vaulderie made it hard for you to break away, until you met your current packmates.  They arranged a Monomancy to have you join their pack and leave your sire's.   You arranged a deal with a ghost to ensure things would go your way.  Your packmates know - they helped you fulfill your side of the bargain after it was all over. But this is NOT something you will ever talk about to anybody.  It's not worth your unlives to do so.  Nowadays you use your abilities as a medium to help your packmates track down Camarilla elders.  You have gotten leads on a couple elders who sleep under San Diego, and you've come to follow them up.  You also hear San Diego is rich with wraiths - this might be a fruitful area for you all."
        ],
